# Demo sample artifacts — TRACKED (tiny ~150-row curated set the HF Space needs).
# These live under sandbox/demo_data/ but are otherwise caught by the artifacts/
# and *.npy / *.index / *.faiss rules above. Unlike the gitignored full-pool
# artifacts/ these are committed so the hosted demo is self-contained. Re-include
# the directory first, then its contents (order matters for git negation).
!sandbox/demo_data/artifacts/
!sandbox/demo_data/artifacts/**